programme.title: Empeños en Luisiana - T1, E03: Mike el limpiabotas
programme.desc: Ponte a calentar motores para ver la llegada de un General Lee, el emblemático coche de la serie 'El sheriff chiflado'.

programme.desc: Prepárate para una buena dosis de dulce mientras los DeRamus tratan de introducirse en el negocio de la apicultura. ¿Acudirán en enjambre y se asegurarán suculentos beneficios?

programme.title: Subastas gigantes - T2, E08: Truro
programme.desc: En la costa este de Canadá, en Nueva Escocia, Truro se erige como la única sede de Ritchie Bros. en la región, allí, las ventas han ido creciendo de forma constante en los últimos años.

programme.title: Trato hecho - T1, E07: Espada de Iwo Jima / Sillas de burdel
programme.desc: Todos los objetos tienen una historia, cuya venta en una subasta puede tener éxito o fracasar. Cindy se hace con dos sillas que podrían proceder de un burdel de Nueva Orleans. Una mujer vende un coche modelo Oldsmobile 442 de 1969 de su hermano. Además, un joven soldado que está recaudando dinero para su boda trae un rifle y una espada japoneses de la Segunda Guerra Mundial, que han estado envueltos durante 60 años en el papel que un soldado utilizó para enviarlos a casa tras la guerra. El arma y la espada podrían llegar a valer mucho dinero... si los desenvuelven. Jon también trabaja en su nueva casa de segunda mano cerca de la tienda de Gallery 63, porque quiere ponerla a punto antes de que la familia venga de visita.

programme.title: Subastas gigantes - T2, E09: Chilliwack
programme.desc: En la pintoresca sede de Ritchie Bros. los trabajadores se afanan para dar el toque final a una subasta al más puro estilo de la Costa Oeste.

programme.title: Subastas gigantes - T2, E10: Spruce View
programme.desc: Después de tres generaciones dedicadas a la agricultura, la familia Wolf de Spruce View, ha decidido vender su granja y con ella, el negocio familiar.

programme.title: Subastas gigantes - T2, E11: Thunder Bay
programme.desc: El norte de Ontario está de suerte ya que la casa de subastas Ritchie Bros. va camino de Thunder Bay para su primera subasta en siete años.

programme.desc: Las asociaciones de compradores se ponen a prueba en una subasta en Brampton. Paul se queja cuando Bogart le pone a dieta. Mientras, Cindy quiere que Rick se ponga una camisa nueva y elegante. Lo que Roy encuentra pone la guinda al pastel.

programme.title: ¿Quién da más? Canadá - T2, E06: Mantén a tus amigos cerca y a los veteranos aún...

programme.title: ¿Quién da más? Canadá - T2, E09: Chin-Chilla Bang Bang

programme.title: Solo en casa

programme.title: King Kong
programme.desc: Peter Jackson nos ofrece una nueva versión de este clásico del cine. Durante la Gran Depresión, Ann Darrow, una actriz de vodevil, se queda sin trabajo. Su suerte parece cambiar cuando conoce a Carl Denham, un empresario que lucha para abrirse camino en el mundo del espectáculo. A ellos se une Jack Driscoll, un autor de teatro. Los tres emprenden un viaje a una remota isla, donde Denham tiene previsto dirigir una película. En una frondosa selva, descubren a King Kong, un gorila gigantesco, y a una tribu de seres prehistóricos que han vivido ocultos durante millones de años.

programme.title: 21 Black Jack
programme.desc: Ben Campbell (Jim Sturgess), un tímido y brillante estudiante del prestigioso Instituto Tecnológico de Massachussets (MIT), recurre a los naipes para poder pagar la matrícula de la universidad. Se le presenta, además, la oportunidad de unirse a un grupo de estudiantes que viajan a Las Vegas cada fin de semana y que están perfectamente preparados para ganar en el black-jack. Bajo la dirección del poco ortodoxo profesor de matemáticas y genio de la estadística Micky Rosa (Kevin Spacey), han conseguido descifrar el código del éxito. Seducido por el dinero y por el estilo de vida de Las Vegas, Ben se coloca al borde de la legalidad.

programme.title: Nigeria’s Miracle Baby Scammers
programme.desc: Africa Eye goes undercover to expose the fertility scammers targeting Nigerian women and fuelling an underground trade in black market babies. Women with fertility issues in Nigeria are being tricked into parting with hundreds of?dollars, duped into believing they?re pregnant and delivering babies that are often trafficked. Africa Eye's undercover investigation exposes one of these scammers, a woman known as Dr Ruth, who guarantees results but says delivery won?t happen without payment for an expensive ?drug?.?The documentary investigates how these scammers prey on women so desperate for a baby that they?believe or choose to ignore the reality that is obvious to most.? We speak to those who have fallen for this scam?and expose the link to baby trafficking. Yemisi Adegoke reports on the crippling stigma of infertility in Nigeria and exposes the criminal networks who profit from it.

programme.sub-title: 2024/25 World Cup Four Hills: Bischofshofen Men's HS142
programme.desc: Action from the men's HS142 event in the concluding World Cup Four Hills meeting, held in Bischofshofen, Austria

programme.title: Dakar Rally
programme.desc: Stage four from Al Henakiyah to Alula

programme.title: Bull
programme.desc: After a decade away, gangland enforcer Bull returns to the streets where he used to do the bidding of his father-in-law, sadistic mob boss Norm. The men fell out when Norm's daughter Gemma developed a drug addiction and Bull demanded sole custody of their son, Aiden. Bull's return ignites the fuse on an orgy of violence targeted at the crime lord and his minions. Thriller, starring Neil Maskell, David Hayman and Tamzin Outhwaite

programme.title: Slice
programme.desc: A pizza delivery driver is murdered on the job, so the city searches for someone to blame. Could it be drug dealers, ghosts or even a werewolf? Horror comedy, starring Chris Parnell, Paul Scheer, Rae Gray and Chance the Rapper

programme.title: Enemy Mine
programme.desc: In the midst of a war between humans and aliens, two space pilots from opposite sides are marooned together on an inhospitable planet and are forced to set aside their mutual animosity to survive. Sci-fi adventure, starring Dennis Quaid, Louis Gossett Jr and Brion James

programme.title: It Came from Beneath the Sea
programme.desc: The captain of a nuclear submarine battles a gigantic octopus threatening to destroy San Francisco. Monster adventure, starring Kenneth Tobey, Faith Domergue and Donald Curtis, with special effects by Ray Harryhausen

programme.title: Decision at Sundown
programme.desc: A gunslinger rides into a backwoods town intent on finding his dead wife's former lover and exacting revenge for her death. The man he blames now has total control of the town and has the sheriff at his beck and call. Undeterred, the drifter offers his enemy an ultimatum - he has until sundown to leave the town or face retribution for his crimes. Western, with Randolph Scott, John Carroll and Andrew Duggan

programme.title: Picnic
programme.desc: A drifter turns up in a small American town looking for a well-off old friend in the hope of borrowing money. However, he causes nothing but trouble for the locals, seducing both his old pal's fiancee and a local schoolteacher. Drama based on William Inge's Pulitzer Prize-winning play, starring William Holden, Cliff Robertson and Kim Novak

programme.title: Flight of the Phoenix
programme.desc: The crew and passengers of a cargo plane are left stranded in the Gobi desert after a crash. They embark on a desperate plan to return to civilisation - by building a new plane out of the wreckage of the old one. Action adventure remake, starring Dennis Quaid, Tyrese Gibson, Giovanni Ribisi, Miranda Otto and Hugh Laurie

programme.title: We Live in Time Interview Special
programme.desc: Stars Andrew Garfield and Florence Pugh - along with director John Crowley - talk about making the Film4-backed romantic drama We Live in Time

programme.title: Mission: Impossible - Ghost Protocol
programme.desc: Secret agent Ethan Hunt and his team are implicated in a bombing at the Kremlin, forcing the American president to declare them fugitives. The spies plan to clear their name by abducting the real terrorist, which leads them into a pursuit around the globe. However, Hunt cannot be sure his colleagues are trustworthy. Action adventure sequel, starring Tom Cruise, Jeremy Renner, Simon Pegg and Paula Patton

A British soldier deployed to Belfast in 1971, almost immediately finds himself caught up in a riot. In the aftermath, he becomes separated from the rest of his unit. Lost and alone at night in a hostile and unfamiliar area, he makes a disturbing journey in search of safety. Thriller, starring Jack O'Connell and Richard Dormer

programme.title: Snatched
programme.desc: After being dumped by her boyfriend before their holiday, Emily Middleton takes her cautious mother Linda with her to Ecuador. However, their lives are soon turned upside down when the pair are kidnapped. Fish-out-of-water comedy, starring Amy Schumer, Goldie Hawn and Joan Cusack

programme.title: Cover Girl
programme.desc: Dancer Rusty Parker works in a small New York club with her choreographer boyfriend Danny McGuire, but gets a taste of fame when she wins a competition to appear on the cover of a prestigious magazine. This in turn leads to her starring in hit musical, though her success has a dramatic effect on her relationship with Danny. Musical comedy, starring Rita Hayworth and Gene Kelly

programme.title: Tora! Tora! Tora!
programme.desc: Fact-based Second World War drama recounting the bombing of Pearl Harbour from both the Japanese and American perspectives, reconstructing the events leading up to the devastating attack on the US naval base in 1941. Starring Martin Balsam, So Yamamura, Joseph Cotten, James Whitmore and Jason Robards

programme.title: Journey to the Center of the Earth
programme.desc: An explorer discovers a prehistoric monster-infested world deep beneath Earth's crust and faces a tough ordeal escaping the predatory attacks of the creatures as he tries to guide his team back to safety. Sci-fi adventure based on Jules Verne's novel, starring Pat Boone, James Mason, Arlene Dahl and Diane Baker

programme.title: Deep Impact
programme.desc: A TV reporter investigating a presidential misdemeanour stumbles on evidence that a comet is on a collision course with Earth, threatening the future of the human race. Meanwhile, an astronaut prepares to lead his crew on a do-or-die mission to intercept the danger. Sci-fi drama, starring Robert Duvall, Tea Leoni, Morgan Freeman and Elijah Wood

programme.title: The G
programme.desc: A mysterious woman seeks revenge on the corrupt legal guardian who destroyed her life. Crime thriller, starring Dale Dickey, Romane Denis and Daniel Brochu

programme.title: The Drop
programme.desc: A Brooklyn bartender secretly provides a service delivering shipments of money to local gangsters. His criminal connections lead to his involvement in a robbery that goes disastrously wrong and digs up the long-buried secrets from his neighbourhood's past. Crime drama based on a short story by Dennis Lehane, starring Tom Hardy, Noomi Rapace and James Gandolfini in his final film role

programme.title: Mona Lisa
programme.desc: A downtrodden small-time crook gets a job as bodyguard and chauffeur to an emotionally bruised call girl, whom he gradually falls in love with. She in turn persuades him to help her save a teenage prostitute from her pimp, a goal that leads to conflict with a brutal gangster. Romantic crime thriller, starring Bob Hoskins, Cathy Tyson, Michael Caine, Robbie Coltrane and Kate Hardie

programme.title: Hangman's Knot
programme.desc: Confederate soldiers wipe out a group of Union troops carrying a shipment of gold, but later learn the Civil War ended the month before, rendering their attack a criminal act. The soldiers go on the run with the loot, but their worries deepen when they are besieged by bandits. Western, starring Randolph Scott, Donna Reed, Lee Marvin and Richard Denning.

programme.title: The 300 Spartans
programme.desc: The ruler of the Persian empire vows to expand his realm by conquering Greece. The king of Sparta steps forward to defend his homeland and the other kingdoms of Greece, but when he is betrayed by a political council, he finds himself without an army and must fend off the vast invading army with a mere 300 warriors. Historical drama, starring Richard Egan, Ralph Richardson and Diane Baker

programme.title: The Moonraker
programme.desc: A foppish royalist nobleman leads a double life as a Roundhead-baiting highwayman. However, after Cromwell's final victory at the battle of Worcester, the dashing hero has to smuggle the son of Charles I to safety in France. Swashbuckling adventure, starring George Baker, Sylvia Syms, Marius Goring, John Le Mesurier and Patrick Troughton

programme.title: Von Ryan's Express
programme.desc: A courageous American colonel with a never-say-die attitude is held in a PoW camp. He boldly sets out to lead a group of Allied prisoners in a daring mass escape bid by hijacking a freight train and fleeing through occupied Italy to Switzerland. Second World War action adventure, starring Frank Sinatra, Trevor Howard, Brad Dexter and James Brolin

programme.title: The Day the Earth Stood Still
programme.desc: An alien arrives on Earth, accompanied by an awesomely powerful robot, on a fateful mission - to decide if the human race deserves to continue - and if not, to wipe it out. The visitor is imprisoned in a military facility, but a scientist helps him escape, hoping to prove that mankind is worth saving. Sci-fi drama remake, starring Keanu Reeves and Jennifer Connelly

programme.title: Mission: Impossible - Rogue Nation
programme.desc: The team of secret agents faces being shut down when the head of the CIA convinces the US Senate that it is too dangerous. The operatives of the Impossible Mission Force become fugitives when they defy orders and plot to bring down a shadowy society of assassins. Spy thriller sequel, starring Tom Cruise, Jeremy Renner, Rebecca Ferguson and Simon Pegg

programme.title: Flag Day
programme.desc: A man lives a double life as a counterfeiter, bank robber and con-man to provide for his daughter. Crime drama based on the true story of Jennifer Vogel. Directed by and starring Sean Penn, with his daughter Dylan playing the role of Jennifer. Also starring Josh Brolin, Regina King and Eddie Marsan

programme.title: xXx: Return Of Xander Cage
programme.desc: Sinopsis film ini dimulai dengan agen yang bernama Augustus Gibbons (Samuel L. Jackson) yang berencana merekrut Neymar untuk menjadi agen xXx. Namun mereka berdua berakhir tewas setelah ada satelit jatuh. Permasalahan kemudian dimulai setelah Xiang (Donnie Yen) bersama empat anggota timnya mencuri sebuah alat canggih yang bernama “Pandora Box” yang dapat mengontrol satelit. Terjadinya hal itu, membuat agen Jane Marke (Toni Collette) menyelidiki kasus tersebut. Agen Jane Marke kemudian menghubungi Xander Cage untuk memintanya kembali bertugas. Selama ini dirinya menjalani kehidupan biasa setelah memalsukan kematiannya untuk menghindari kejaran musuh. Ia bersedia untuk kembali bertugas setelah mengetahui Agen Gibbons meninggal. Saat itu juga, ia meninggalkan Republik Dominika untuk pergi ke London. Xander Cage akhirnya membentuk sebuah tim yang beranggotakan seorang penembak jitu Adele Wolff (Ruby Rose), DJ Harvard “Nicks” Zhou (Kris Wu), supir travel Tennyson “The Torch” (Roy McCane), dan spesialis senjata Becky Clearidge (Nina Dobrev). Namun mereka terjerat ke dalam sebuah konspirasi besar dan kini mereka harus mengungkap konspirasi tersebut yang dilakukan oleh para pemimpin dunia yang membuat musuh mereka semakinn bertambah. Mereka juga harus mengejar waktu sebelum Xiang meledakkan satelitnya.

programme.title: Come Dine with Me
programme.desc: Children's food educator Beth Stephens hosts the first dinner party in Lowestoft, Suffolk, where she plans to impress her guests - caravan site owner Ray, beauty therapist Polly, housing officer Jonalt and ASBO officer Rachel - with locally sourced seasonal food. programme.title: Come Dine with Me

programme.title: Come Dine with Me

programme.title: Come Dine with Me

programme.title: Come Dine with Me
programme.desc: The final dinner party in Suffolk is hosted by anti-social behaviour officer Rachel, who hopes to win over her guests with an evening of comfort food and a few tricks up her sleeve. programme.title: Four in a Bed

programme.title: Four in a Bed
programme.desc: Julia Grant hosts the third round of the competition in Spain at her Benidorm B&B The Queens Hotel. programme.title: Four in a Bed

programme.title: Four in a Bed

programme.title: Car S.O.S.

programme.title: Grand Designs

programme.title: Un tipo serio
programme.desc: De la mano de los hermanos Coen nos llega esta celebrada comedia nominada a dos Premios Óscar incluyendo el de mejor película. Con un humor áspero y una brillante interpretación de Michael Stuhlbarg, sigue la debacle vital de un neurótico profesor de física cuya vida se pone patas arriba de la noche a la mañana. Medio-oeste americano, 1967. Larry Gopnik es un profesor de física que ve cómo de la noche a la mañana su vida se derrumba. Es un hombre bueno, un marido fiel y afectuoso, un buen padre y un profesor serio, pero, de repente, todo en su vida empieza a ir mal. Su mujer lo abandona sin explicaciones, y el amante de ella lo convence para que deje su casa y se mude a un motel por el bien de los niños. Además, su carrera profesional se ve amenazada cuando comienza a recibir una serie de anónimos con acusaciones contra su persona.
